      <title>黄金通过了2,900美元，以记录特朗普关税Spur Spur Haven购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/gold-xauusd-edges-higher-toward-record-as-trump-tariffs-aid-haven-bids</link>
